    "en": {
      "title": "Pathum Kerner remanded to 4th August",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Social Media Activist Pathum Kerner was remanded to the 4th of August by the Colombo Magistrate's Court.",
        "Additional Magistrate Harshana Kekunawela ordered for the suspect to be produced in an identifiation parade on that day.",
        "Pathuk Kerner was arrested on Thursday (28) after he surrendered to the Colombo Crimes Division.",
        "Police Spokesperson SSP Attorney-at-Law Nihal Thalduwa said on Thursday (28) that the arrest of Pathum Kerner was releated to the protest at Polduwa Junction, Battaramulla where unruly incidents took place."
      ],
